== English ==

=== Verb ===

# Near-synonym of [[want]], but more formal in tone
#: ''I desire to speak with you''

==== Translations ====

*German: [[begehren]]

=== Noun ===

# Someone or something wished for
#: ''It is my desire to speak with you''
#: ''You're my heart's desire''
# (''uncountable'') Strong attraction, particularly romantic
#: ''His desire for her kept him awake at night''
# (''uncountable'') The feeling of desire
#: ''Too much desire can seriously affect ones judgement''

